{"tid":1683131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我上學好累 快要自殺 (我臺灣的","createTime":"2019-10-30T13:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T15:17:47.000Z","uid":200873,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1096f7d39c5a7e4d50ac71b2717eb521ec850fce","tid":1683131,"uid":200873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"好啦 我也不知道我過來香港發文作什麼<br />\n不過是想要紓解下<br />\n<br />\n事情是這樣<br />\n台灣是9月開學 我在9月中的時候崩潰(整個人到現在還未完全恢復)<br />\n我也不知道 只覺得到現在心還好累<br />\n沒有心情作什麼事<br />\n(不過我到是發了3篇改歌<br />\n<br />\n有沒有人幫幫我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dd6fc3bc939d2a24ab49e0c1e5fdb0a933f4f6","tid":1683131,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:22:51.000Z","msg":"「正能量雞湯」曾經我也想過一了百了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679955</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n臺灣的巴打你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n這是我前兩天寫的正能量文<br />\n希望能夠幫助你"},{"pid":"a3851c15573752a5359abc597a4809a923cc5f66","tid":1683131,"uid":200873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90dd6fc3bc939d2a24ab49e0c1e5fdb0a933f4f6","tid":1683131,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:22:51.000Z","msg":"「正能量雞湯」曾經我也想過一了百了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679955</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n臺灣的巴打你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n這是我前兩天寫的正能量文<br />\n希望能夠幫助你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"謝謝你<br />\n我這幾天都是憂鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期一晚上還哭了一整個晚上